high_descs: Turn and go left and stand in front of the spatula on the counter.
Pick the spatula up off of the counter.
Go right and then left to stand in front of the sink.
Put the spatula in the sink, turn the water on, turn the water off, and take the spatula out.
Turn around and face the drawer to the left of the stove.
Put the spatula in the drawer to the left of the stove and shut it.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spatula in a drawer.

high_descs: Go to the end of the island by the window.
Pick up the spatula near the edge.
Take the spatula to the sink.
Clean the spatula in the sink.
Turn and take the clean spatula to the counter on the left of the stove.
Put the clean spatula in the drawer under the blue credit card.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spatula in a drawer.

high_descs: Turn left, go to the window, turn left, go straight, turn to the kitchen island when it is on the left.
Take the spatula from the island.
Turn right, go straight, turn left, go straight, turn to the sink when it is on the left.
Put the spatula in the sink, turn the water on then off, take the spatula from the sink.
Turn around and face the counter to the left of the oven.
Put the spatula in the top drawer underneath the counter to the left of the oven.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spatula in a drawer.
